        <header class="article-header">
            <h4 class="post-upperdek">
      Throwing more hardware at the problem    &mdash;
</h4>
            <h1 itemprop="headline">Wear OS “Hybrid” design has two OSes, two CPUs, “100 hour” battery life</h1>
            <h2 itemprop="description">Wear OS + Snapdragon uses too much power, so what if we just turned it off?</h2>
            <section class="post-meta">

  
<p class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
      <a itemprop="url" href="https://arstechnica.com/author/ronamadeo/"  rel="author" ><span itemprop="name">Ron Amadeo</span></a>
    -    <time class="date" data-time="1708981680" datetime="2024-02-26T21:08:00+00:00">Feb 26, 2024 9:08 pm UTC</time>
</p>

  
</section>        </header>
